# =============================================================================
# PARA DESENVOLVIMENTO LOCAL (use localhost)
# =============================================================================
# Copie as linhas abaixo para .env.local se quiser rodar localmente:
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=http://localhost:54321
# SUPABASE_URL=http://localhost:54321
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=anon-key-local
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=service-role-key-local
# NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
# NODE_ENV=development

# =============================================================================
# CONFIGURAR NO EASYPANEL
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. Applications > clickup > Settings
# 2. Environment Variables — adicione todas as variáveis acima
# 3. Build Command:
#    npm install --legacy-peer-deps && npm run build
# 4. Start Command:
#    npm start
# 5. Port: 3000
# 6. Deploy
#
# 7. APÓS deploy bem-sucedido, configure LogTo:
#    - Console LogTo > Applications > Redirect URIs
#    - Adicione: https://seu-dominio.com/app/callback
#    - Post Sign-out: https://seu-dominio.com/login
#    - Save changes
#
# =============================================================================
